{"tid":2151003,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我紋左WENDY係JER仔上面","createTime":"2020-08-11T07:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T14:35:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"531ce60edc1912a9375e4676c67416978f7574ef","tid":2151003,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:34:49.000Z","msg":"阿導有個女朋友名字叫WENDY，阿導非常愛他的女朋友，於是就將女朋友的名字刺青在他的寶貝上面，平時垂軟時，只看得到&ldquo;WY&rdquo;兩個字。<br />\n<br />\n有一天，阿導去美國旅行在公共澡堂裏遇著一個黑人， 黑人看到他寶貝上有&ldquo;WY&rdquo;兩個字，就問他那是什麼意思......<br />\n<br />\n阿導說：「這是我女朋友的名字。」並且將寶貝弄翹起來， 讓&ldquo;WY&rdquo;變成WENDY給他看。<br />\n<br />\n這時，他看到黑人的老二上也有&ldquo;WY&rdquo;兩個字，他很好奇的問他：「你的女朋友也叫WENDY嗎?」<br />\n<br />\n黑人說：「不是。」阿導一直問那黑人到底是什麼，可是黑人一直不肯透露。<br />\n<br />\n阿導說：「這樣好了，我給你十元美金，你給我看你的刺青。」黑人答應了，於是黑人就打了個手槍......<br />\n<br />\n寶貝上的文字 就出現了：WELCOME TO THE UNITED STATE OF AMERICA， HAVE ANICE DAY。"},{"pid":"cecda9f7797f3c28b338a211ec82380a00f4d2c7","tid":2151003,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:35:29.000Z","msg":"@牙喪"},{"pid":"842b9d1776696cea65ce1df61dc03255c7f2b772","tid":2151003,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e0fc86957ae3687b0496ac671661ad6ff6513a","tid":2151003,"uid":203454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"Haha"},{"pid":"fb8adeb2e775af6f58006b1ca40c4337bbce2bb5","tid":2151003,"uid":52211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T07:38:17.000Z","m